-I do like you.

00:05:25.756 --> 00:05:26.430
I do.

00:05:26.430 --> 00:05:27.950
I like you very much.

00:05:27.950 --> 00:05:29.180
-Well then why--

00:05:29.180 --> 00:05:30.320
-We just can't.

00:05:30.320 --> 00:05:30.980
OK?

00:05:30.980 --> 00:05:31.810
We can't.

00:05:35.128 --> 00:05:37.498
-But I want you, David.

00:05:37.498 --> 00:05:38.650
-No, you don't, Bianca.

00:05:38.650 --> 00:05:39.650
