And in the pitch
document, he says,

00:10:57.450 --> 00:11:00.870
"Suddenly the police bureaucracy
is amoral, dysfunctional,

00:11:00.870 --> 00:11:03.730
and criminality in the
form of the drug culture

00:11:03.730 --> 00:11:07.320
is just as suddenly
a bureaucracy."

